<font face="arial" Size="-1" color="caffb0"><b>When a mob is rooted it will ALWAYS attack the nearest player. Be aware around Earth Pets, those root so MT will have to be closest, all otehrs back off.
If you run out of taunt when grouped with a rogue, root the mob and have someone stand close. Then the rogue can backstab.</b><br></font>
